caption.p: The time course analysis of gene expression in different treatment groups. ( A) Protopine 6-hydroxylase (P6H). ( B) Dihydrobenzophenanthridine oxidase (DBOX). Asterisks denote the significant changes (Tukey’s test, * means P < 0.05, ** means P < 0.01, *** means P < 0.005, **** means P < 0.001) compared with 0 h group.
